<%= erb :navigation %>

<div class="scene">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="center-horiz">
      <h1 class="title">Work</h1>
    </div>
    <img class="mountain-image" src="images/mountain_range.png">
    <div class="particle particle-1"></div>
    <div class="particle particle-2"></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="work-content">
    <div id="earlybird" class="row">
      <div class="col s12 m5 l5">
        <img class="eb-image"src="images/mountain_range.png">
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m6 l6 push-m1 push-l1">
        <h4 class="custom-teal">EarlyBird</h4>
        <p>
          A conference management tool for <%= link_to "Viget", '//www.viget.com' %>.
          I collaborated with other developers, designers and UX researchers to
          redesign the user dashboard / conference request flow and upgrade the
          app from Rails 4 to 6.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="trail-buddy" class="row">
      <div class="col s12 m6 l6">
        <h4 class="custom-teal">Trail Buddy</h4>
        <p>
          A proof-of-concept tool that predicts trail conditions based off
          previous weather and soil data. This was built in 48 hours during
          a company hackathon at <%= link_to "Viget", '//www.viget.com' %>. We
          used machine learning and 5 external APIs.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m5 l5 push-m1 push-l1">
        <img class="trail-buddy-image"src="images/mountain_range.png">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="finance-tracker" class="row">
      <div class="col s12 m5 l5">
        <img class="ft-image"src="images/mountain_range.png">
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m6 l6 push-m1 push-l1">
        <h4 class="custom-teal">Finance Tracker</h4>
        <p>
          A Robinhood clone without monetary transactions. My first project
          using external APIs and data visualization built in Rails.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="personal-site" class="row">
      <div class="col s12 m6 l6">
        <h4 class="custom-teal">Personal Website</h4>
        <p>
          A test in design. This site was built on Sinatra and uses the front
          end framework Materialize for basic styling and Animejs for animations.
          All graphics were made in GIMP.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m5 l5 push-m1 push-l1">
        <img class="personal-site-gimp-image"src="images/mountain_range.png">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="haxxor-news" class="row">
      <div class="col s12 m5 l5">
        <img class="haxxor-image"src="images/mountain_range.png">
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m6 l6 push-m1 push-l1">
        <h4 class="custom-teal">Haxxor News</h4>
        <p>
          A Hacker News clone built in Rails. This was built with custom authentication,
          pagination, threaded commenting, and voting.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>



<div class="full-width center-horiz bottom">
  <%= erb :footer %>
</div>
